Name: Load Cube - Planning PRO - Billable Hours
Code@Code.link: Load Cube - Planning PRO - Billable Hours.ti

DataSource.query:
SELECT 
[Project Geo Value] vGeo, 
[Timecard Hours Total] vValue, 
[Budget Billable Type] vBillableType, 
[Timecard Resource Type Consolidated] vTimecardResourceType, 
[Project Group] vMarketSegment,
[Budget Override Project Practice] vBudgetOverrideProjectPractice,
[Assignment Billable] vAssignmentBillable
from [ACS_Insights_Timecard_Actuals_Final]
WHERE
[Project Group] <> 'Tune Up'
and [Timecard End Date Ops Year-Quarter] = '?pQuarter?'
and [Budget Billable Type] IN ('T&M', 'Deliverable Acceptance', 'Fixed Fee', 'LFS', 'Ratable')
and [Timecard Hours Category 1] = 'Commissionable Productive'
and [Timecard Status] IN ('Approved', 'Submitted')
